Protocol implementation notes
================================================================================

This project implements IBM 5250 (TN5250/TN5250E) and IBM i Host Server network
protocols. These are wire protocols: their byte layouts, constants, and message
sequences are factual descriptions of how systems interoperate, not creative
expression.

IBM's JTOpen / IBM Toolbox for Java (including its "jtopenlite" component) was
consulted as documentation for these protocols. JTOpen is licensed under the
IBM Public License 1.0. No JTOpen source code has been copied, translated, or
otherwise incorporated into this repository, and no JTOpen source is
distributed with it. Where a module implements a protocol also implemented by
JTOpen, a source-reference comment names the corresponding JTOpen class or
method so that readers can locate the equivalent upstream description.

